                            <comment id="15146456" author="chenheng" created="Sun, 14 Feb 2016 09:18:11 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;IMO some monitor threads need to catch throwable.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="15146712" author="busbey" created="Sun, 14 Feb 2016 20:11:11 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Exceptions to a rule are likely to exist, and the judgement of our committers should be able to handle identifying appropriate uses and ensuring that we&apos;re handling things correctly (for example making sure we&apos;re not discarding Errors).&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
